    "description": "<p>From startup to key industry player, H.A.M. Creations has evolved to become a creative production company of choice. Today, the company offers a complete suite of services–visual merchandising and communication, experiential activation, large format printing, and events production–beyond Singapore to the Asia-Pacific Region.​</p>\n<p>​</p>\n<p>H.A.M. Creations is supported by over&nbsp;30 dedicated individuals that make up our team of project managers, graphic &amp;&nbsp;3D designers,&nbsp;carpenters, print operators, and installers.​</p>\n<p>​​</p>\n<p>We’ve built a fine reputation on our finesse and quality of work for global luxury brands, which is endorsed by a decades of client satisfaction. Looking forward to the future, we are constantly improving our capabilities by embracing new technologies that enable new production methods and build&nbsp;directions.​</p>",
